            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                <ab>
                 <lb n="1"/><w lemma="οὐδείς">Οὐδεὶς </w>
                 <lb n="2"/><w lemma="ἄξιος"><choice><orig>ά</orig><reg>ἄ</reg></choice>ξιος</w> τ<choice><orig>ω</orig><reg>ῶ</reg></choice>ν 
                 <lb n="3"/><w lemma="συνδῶ">σ<hi rend="ligature">ην</hi>δε
                 <lb n="4" break="no"/>δεμέ
                 <lb n="5" break="no"/>νων</w> τ<hi rend="ligature">α<choice><orig>ι</orig><reg>ῖ</reg></choice></hi>ς 
                 <lb n="6"/><w lemma="σαρκική"><expan><abbr>σαρκυ</abbr><ex>καῖς</ex></expan></w>
                 </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>Pending</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>No one of those who are tied to carnal (desires and pleasures is worthy to approach, draw near, or serve You, glorious King).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. The words συνδεδεμένων and σαρκικαῖς are misspelled. The inscription is from the Prayer of the Cherubic Hymn. </p>
            </div>
